{
  "openapi": "3.0.3",
  "info": {
    "title": "WebSocket 直播场次改造",
    "version": "v1",
    "description": "本文件描述 WebSocket 入口在「直播场次（live_session）维度」改造后的契约：\n\n- 在原有 `/ws/auctions/{auction_id}`（直接拍卖流，保留兼容）基础上，新增 `/ws/live-rooms/{room_id}`，由后端解析 `room.active_auction_id` 路由到当前活跃拍品并注入 `liveSessionId`。\n- 帧 envelope 在原有 `type/requestId/seq/ack/payload` 基础上新增 `liveSessionId` 字段，供按场次维度反查/广播使用。\n- 关播时 `Hub.BroadcastSessionEnd` 会向当前 `liveSessionId` 下所有客户端推送 `live_session.ended` 帧；客户端可据此自行断开或等待 close。\n\n鉴权方式与 REST 一致：JWT Bearer，由路由层 `AuthMiddleware()` 统一校验；通过后将 userID 注入到 WS Client。注意：这些 WS 端点不属于 `/api/v1` 前缀，直接挂在根路径。"
  },
  "servers": [
    {
      "url": "http://localhost:8888",
      "description": "Local"
    }
  ],
  "tags": [
    {
      "name": "WebSocket",
      "description": "实时推送通道（HTTP/1.1 Upgrade -> WebSocket）"
    }
  ],
  "paths": {
    "/ws/auctions/{auction_id}": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["WebSocket"],
        "summary": "订阅指定拍品的实时事件流（兼容入口）",
        "description": "WebSocket Upgrade 端点。客户端需通过 HTTP/1.1 `Upgrade: websocket` 协议升级握手；握手成功后服务端返回 `101 Switching Protocols`，随后通过 WebSocket 文本帧承载 `Envelope` 协议双向通信。\n\n- 鉴权：与 REST 一致的 JWT Bearer，匿名连接 `userId` 默认为 `anonymous`，但出价等需鉴权动作仍会被服务端校验。\n- 订阅语义：连接成功后该 client 自动订阅到 `auction_id` 对应房间。\n- 重放：`?lastSeq=` 查询参数可在重连时请求增量重放；超出事件窗口时服务端会回推 `room.snapshot_required` 让客户端切换为快照拉取。\n- 不属于 `/api/v1` 前缀，路径直接挂在根路径下。",
        "operationId": "wsAuctionSubscribe",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "auction_id",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "schema": { "type": "integer", "format": "uint64" },
            "description": "拍品 ID（auction_lot.auction_id）"
          },
          {
            "name": "lastSeq",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": { "type": "integer", "format": "int64", "minimum": 0 },
            "description": "客户端最近收到的 seq；重连时携带可触发服务端按区间重放。"
          },
          {
            "name": "Upgrade",
            "in": "header",
            "required": true,
            "schema": { "type": "string", "enum": ["websocket"] }
          },
          {
            "name": "Connection",
            "in": "header",
            "required": true,
            "schema": { "type": "string", "enum": ["Upgrade"] }
          },
          {
            "name": "Sec-WebSocket-Version",
            "in": "header",
            "required": true,
            "schema": { "type": "string", "enum": ["13"] }
          },
          {
            "name": "Sec-WebSocket-Key",
            "in": "header",
            "required": true,
            "schema": { "type": "string" }
          }
        ],
        "security": [{ "BearerAuth": [] }],
        "responses": {
          "101": {
            "description": "协议升级成功，转入 WebSocket 帧流（参考 schemas.Envelope）。",
            "headers": {
              "Upgrade": { "schema": { "type": "string", "enum": ["websocket"] } },
              "Connection": { "schema": { "type": "string", "enum": ["Upgrade"] } },
              "Sec-WebSocket-Accept": { "schema": { "type": "string" } }
            }
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "auction_id 非法",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse" }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": { "description": "未鉴权或 token 无效" },
          "500": {
            "description": "Hub Subscribe 失败等内部错误",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse" }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/ws/live-rooms/{room_id}": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["WebSocket"],
        "summary": "订阅直播间当前活跃拍品 + 直播场次（场次维度入口）",
        "description": "WebSocket Upgrade 端点。后端通过 `LiveRoomService.ActiveAuctionAndSession(roomID)` 一次性解析出 `(activeAuctionId, liveSessionId)`：\n\n- 当 `activeAuctionId == 0`：返回 `409 + 31005 直播间当前无在拍品`，不进入 Upgrade。\n- 当 `activeAuctionId != 0`：在 Hub 中为该客户端构造带 `LiveSessionID` 的 Client（`NewClientWithSession`），自动加入 `auctionId -> Room` 与 `liveSessionId -> Clients` 两张反查表。\n- 闭播路径：`LiveSessionService.CloseSession` 触发 `Hub.BroadcastSessionEnd(liveSessionId)`，向当前会话下所有客户端推送 `type=live_session.ended` 帧；客户端收到后应主动断开或等待服务端 close。\n\n鉴权与 `/ws/auctions/{auction_id}` 一致；同样不属于 `/api/v1` 前缀。",
        "operationId": "wsLiveRoomSubscribe",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "room_id",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "schema": { "type": "integer", "format": "uint64" },
            "description": "直播间 ID（live_room.id）"
          },
          {
            "name": "lastSeq",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": { "type": "integer", "format": "int64", "minimum": 0 },
            "description": "重放游标，与 /ws/auctions 一致。"
          },
          {
            "name": "Upgrade",
            "in": "header",
            "required": true,
            "schema": { "type": "string", "enum": ["websocket"] }
          },
          {
            "name": "Connection",
            "in": "header",
            "required": true,
            "schema": { "type": "string", "enum": ["Upgrade"] }
          },
          {
            "name": "Sec-WebSocket-Version",
            "in": "header",
            "required": true,
            "schema": { "type": "string", "enum": ["13"] }
          },
          {
            "name": "Sec-WebSocket-Key",
            "in": "header",
            "required": true,
            "schema": { "type": "string" }
          }
        ],
        "security": [{ "BearerAuth": [] }],
        "responses": {
          "101": {
            "description": "协议升级成功；连接已绑定 `(auctionId, liveSessionId)`。后续通过 WebSocket 帧（参考 schemas.Envelope）双向通信。",
            "headers": {
              "Upgrade": { "schema": { "type": "string", "enum": ["websocket"] } },
              "Connection": { "schema": { "type": "string", "enum": ["Upgrade"] } },
              "Sec-WebSocket-Accept": { "schema": { "type": "string" } }
            }
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "room_id 非法",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse" }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": { "description": "未鉴权或 token 无效" },
          "404": {
            "description": "直播间不存在",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse" }
              }
            }
          },
          "409": {
            "description": "直播间当前无在拍品（activeAuctionId 为 0）。错误码 31005。",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse" },
                "example": {
                  "code": 31005,
                  "message": "直播间当前无在拍品"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "500": {
            "description": "服务初始化未注入 LiveRoomService 或 Hub Subscribe 失败",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse" }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/ws/live-sessions/{sessionId}": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["WebSocket"],
        "summary": "订阅直播场次当前活跃拍品事件流",
        "description": "WebSocket Upgrade 端点。客户端直接以直播场次 ID 建连，后端按 `live_session.id` 找到该场次当前活跃拍品并绑定 `(auctionId, liveSessionId)`：\n\n- 当场次不存在：返回 `404`，不进入 Upgrade。\n- 当场次当前无活跃拍品：返回 `409 + 31005 直播场次当前无在拍品`，不进入 Upgrade。\n- 当存在活跃拍品：客户端自动加入 `auctionId -> Room` 与 `liveSessionId -> Clients` 两张反查表，后续可接收出价、拍品状态与 `live_session.ended` 等场次维度事件。\n\n鉴权与 `/ws/auctions/{auction_id}` 一致；同样不属于 `/api/v1` 前缀。",
        "operationId": "wsLiveSessionSubscribe",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "sessionId",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "schema": { "type": "integer", "format": "uint64" },
            "description": "直播场次 ID（live_session.id）"
          },
          {
            "name": "lastSeq",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": { "type": "integer", "format": "int64", "minimum": 0 },
            "description": "重放游标，与 /ws/auctions 一致。"
          },
          {
            "name": "Upgrade",
            "in": "header",
            "required": true,
            "schema": { "type": "string", "enum": ["websocket"] }
          },
          {
            "name": "Connection",
            "in": "header",
            "required": true,
            "schema": { "type": "string", "enum": ["Upgrade"] }
          },
          {
            "name": "Sec-WebSocket-Version",
            "in": "header",
            "required": true,
            "schema": { "type": "string", "enum": ["13"] }
          },
          {
            "name": "Sec-WebSocket-Key",
            "in": "header",
            "required": true,
            "schema": { "type": "string" }
          }
        ],
        "security": [{ "BearerAuth": [] }],
        "responses": {
          "101": {
            "description": "协议升级成功；连接已绑定 `(auctionId, liveSessionId)`。后续通过 WebSocket 帧（参考 schemas.Envelope）双向通信。",
            "headers": {
              "Upgrade": { "schema": { "type": "string", "enum": ["websocket"] } },
              "Connection": { "schema": { "type": "string", "enum": ["Upgrade"] } },
              "Sec-WebSocket-Accept": { "schema": { "type": "string" } }
            }
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "sessionId 非法",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse" }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": { "description": "未鉴权或 token 无效" },
          "404": {
            "description": "直播场次不存在",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse" }
              }
            }
          },
          "409": {
            "description": "直播场次当前无在拍品（activeAuctionId 为 0）。错误码 31005。",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse" },
                "example": {
                  "code": 31005,
                  "message": "直播场次当前无在拍品"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "500": {
            "description": "服务初始化未注入 LiveSessionService 或 Hub Subscribe 失败",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse" }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "components": {
    "securitySchemes": {
      "BearerAuth": {
        "type": "http",
        "scheme": "bearer",
        "bearerFormat": "JWT",
        "description": "与 REST API 共用同一份 JWT。WebSocket 升级请求的 Authorization 头由 AuthMiddleware 统一校验。"
      }
    },
    "schemas": {
      "Envelope": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "WebSocket 双向帧统一信封。所有入站/出站帧（含心跳、订阅、出价、关播等）都包装为该结构。`liveSessionId` 字段在场次入口连接里由服务端注入，客户端无需主动设置。",
        "properties": {
          "type": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "帧类型；下方 `EventType` 列举了实际广播 / 应答中出现过的常量。",
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/EventType"
          },
          "requestId": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "客户端请求 ID（幂等键）；服务端 Ack 帧会原样回填。"
          },
          "seq": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64",
            "description": "房间内单调递增序号；客户端可据此做重放游标。"
          },
          "ack": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "description": "是否为 Ack 帧。`type=ack` 时为 true。"
          },
          "liveSessionId": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "uint64",
            "description": "所属直播场次 ID。仅在 `live_session.ended` 等场次维度帧上出现；普通房间帧（如 bid.accepted）目前由服务端不强制设置。"
          },
          "payload": {
            "description": "帧载荷（原始 JSON）；不同 type 的载荷形状由具体事件决定。",
            "oneOf": [
              { "type": "object" },
              { "type": "array" },
              { "type": "string" },
              { "type": "number" },
              { "type": "boolean" },
              { "type": "null" }
            ]
          }
        },
        "required": ["type"]
      },
      "EventType": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "WebSocket 帧 type 枚举。来源：`internal/transport/ws/hub.go`、`internal/transport/http/ws_handler.go`、`internal/service/{auction,bid,hammer}.go` 中实际广播 / 应答常量。",
        "enum": [
          "ack",
          "error",
          "ping",
          "pong",
          "heartbeat",
          "heartbeat.ack",
          "subscribe",
          "subscribed",
          "room.subscribe",
          "room.subscribed",
          "room.unsubscribe",
          "room.unsubscribed",
          "room.online",
          "room.snapshot_required",
          "announcement",
          "bid.place",
          "bid.ack",
          "bid.accepted",
          "bid.rejected",
          "auction.started",
          "auction.closed",
          "live_session.ended"
        ]
      },
      "BidPlacePayload": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "入站 `bid.place` 帧载荷。WS 服务端会调用 `BidService.Place(...)` 处理。",
        "properties": {
          "auctionId": { "type": "integer", "format": "uint64" },
          "price": { "type": "integer", "format": "int64", "description": "出价金额（分）。" },
          "requestId": { "type": "string", "description": "幂等键；缺省时回退到 envelope.requestId。" },
          "idempotencyKey": { "type": "string", "description": "兼容旧字段，与 requestId 互为别名。" }
        },
        "required": ["price"]
      },
      "BidAckPayload": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "出站 `bid.ack` 帧载荷。",
        "properties": {
          "accepted": { "type": "boolean" },
          "code": { "type": "integer", "description": "服务端业务错误码（accepted=false 时出现）。" },
          "reason": { "type": "string", "description": "拒绝原因或人类可读信息。" },
          "auctionId": { "type": "integer", "format": "uint64" },
          "currentPrice": { "type": "integer", "format": "int64" },
          "seq": { "type": "integer", "format": "int64" },
          "streamId": { "type": "string" },
          "event": { "type": "string", "enum": ["bid.accepted", "bid.rejected"] }
        }
      },
      "RoomSubscribePayload": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "`room.subscribe` / `room.unsubscribe` / `room.subscribed` / `room.unsubscribed` 共用载荷。",
        "properties": {
          "auctionId": { "type": "integer", "format": "uint64" }
        }
      },
      "RoomOnlinePayload": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "`room.online` 在线人数变更广播载荷。",
        "properties": {
          "auctionId": { "type": "integer", "format": "uint64" },
          "online": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 0 }
        }
      },
      "RoomSnapshotRequiredPayload": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "`room.snapshot_required` 触发条件：客户端 lastSeq 落在事件窗口外，需要走快照拉取。",
        "properties": {
          "auctionId": { "type": "integer", "format": "uint64" },
          "lastSeq": { "type": "integer", "format": "int64" },
          "reason": { "type": "string", "enum": ["EVENT_WINDOW_EXPIRED"] }
        }
      },
      "HeartbeatAckPayload": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "`heartbeat.ack` / `ping` 载荷。",
        "properties": {
          "ts": { "type": "integer", "format": "int64", "description": "服务端时间戳（毫秒）。" }
        }
      },
      "LiveSessionEndedPayload": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "`live_session.ended` 帧载荷，由 `Hub.BroadcastSessionEnd` 推送给当前 `liveSessionId` 下所有客户端。具体字段由调用方自定义，下列为典型字段。",
        "properties": {
          "liveSessionId": { "type": "integer", "format": "uint64" },
          "liveRoomId": { "type": "integer", "format": "uint64" },
          "closedAt": { "type": "string", "format": "date-time" },
          "lotsTotal": { "type": "integer" },
          "lotsSold": { "type": "integer" },
          "lotsUnsold": { "type": "integer" },
          "bidCount": { "type": "integer" },
          "gmvCent": { "type": "integer", "format": "int64" }
        }
      },
      "ErrorPayload": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "`type=error` 帧载荷。",
        "properties": {
          "message": { "type": "string" }
        }
      },
      "AckPayload": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "`type=ack` 帧载荷。",
        "properties": {
          "requestId": { "type": "string" },
          "seq": { "type": "integer", "format": "int64" }
        }
      },
      "HubStats": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Hub 实例运行状态快照（来源：`Hub.Stats()`，仅运维 / 调试用途，不直接通过 WS 帧推送）。",
        "properties": {
          "rooms": { "type": "integer", "description": "Room 数量。" },
          "clients": { "type": "integer", "description": "全部 Room 累计的 client 数量。" },
          "liveSessions": { "type": "integer", "description": "当前挂载的 liveSessionId 数。" },
          "liveSessionId": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "key=liveSessionId，value=该 session 下挂载的 client 数量。",
            "additionalProperties": { "type": "integer" }
          }
        }
      },
      "ErrorResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "REST 风格错误响应；用于 Upgrade 之前的握手错误（如 409 直播间无在拍品）。",
        "properties": {
          "code": { "type": "integer" },
          "message": { "type": "string" },
          "trace_id": { "type": "string" }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
